 <span data-ttu-id="46e5e-102"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EventParameterType> jest używana podczas tworzenia <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> obiektu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46e5e-102"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EventParameterType> is used when constructing a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="46e5e-103">Wystąpienie <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EventParameterType> przekazany jako `parameterType` argument do konstruktora dla <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> określa sposób `param2` argumentów konstruktora (która musi być `System.IntPtr`) jest interpretowany.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46e5e-103">An instance of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EventParameterType> passed as the `parameterType` argument to the constructor for <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> specifies how the `param2` argument of the constructor (which must be a `System.IntPtr`) is interpreted.</span></span>  
  
